item.title: Do I need to Change This?

item.description:
@Ashton51 wrote:

  1. Wrong section, For client help please post here.
  2. Both of them should be set to the no-ip address if you want someone else from a different address to connect. Or you can set them both to 127.0.0.1 if only you will be connecting to the server.
